originalText.text: Catherine has been a godsend in helping myself lead a pain free life after suffering from a neck injury and lower back pain over the years. Her great ability to properly diagnose and treat pain and a lack of mobility is remarkable. Her training and work experience is beyond reproach. Years of working with clients at the prestigious HSS Integrative Care Center in Manhattan has prepared her for private practice. Read her testimonials. See how many people because of her dedication she has helped and will never forget her.

originalText.text: Catherine has a beautiful loving and calm presence that made me feel at ease straight away. She helped me improve my posture and she gave me a fantastic reflexology session. I had never had reflexology done before, so I wasn't sure what to expect. It was a very holistic experience as I felt Catherine's presence, love and genuine kindness through her hands and talented touch. I was rejuvenated by the session, it improved my sleep and I woke up the next day a brand new woman! Thank you so much for sharing your gift with the world. I look forward to our next session.

originalText.text: I have been seeing Catherine for various purposes for the past few years.  She is excellent and my wife who also uses her agrees.  I have back issues and due to an accident had major knee surgery. For both, she has been instrumental in feeling better.  She is also a great general masseuse for just simply feeling good.

originalText.text: I was Catherine’s client for many years until I moved to Colorado. I started seeing her when I had major issues with my traps and neck. The doctor I was seeing wanted to just numb the pain, but she recognized that there was a bigger issue and referred me to an amazing physical therapist. Together the two of them are the reason why I’m no longer living with daily pain.  Sessions with her were not standard massages, she used Neuromuscular and Neurokinetic  Therapy to help me.  She set the bar so high I’m having a hard time finding a suitable replacement after my move.

originalText.text:
Catherine is my go-to person when I have a sports injury. I am a runner so I regularly suffer an injury and what sets Catherine apart as a massage therapist is her time off the massage table. She invests in finding the root of the problem before she gets to work on it, then provides a road to recovery and suggestions for how to prevent a recurrence.
I used to go to sports doctors before I found Catherine, but now I go straight to her. Every single time she makes me feel as if I am a superstar athlete with the detailed attention she provides that offers a quick and healthy way to get back to being active.
